Statue of King Sejong the Great
address: 172 Sejong-daero, Sejongno, Jongno-gu, Seoul, South Korea
description: The bronze statue of King Sejong is located in Seoul, South Korea. It is 6.2 meters high and weighs 20 tons. King Sejong was the fourth king of the Joseon Dynasty of the Lee family and one of the most outstanding monarchs of the Joseon Dynasty. His main achievements included the promulgation of "Hunminjeongeum".
